   Captain Brad's Coastal Kitchen24435 Tomball Parkway, TomballS P's
   review: This, by far, is the best restaurant! The food is fresh and
   amazing. The service is friendly and attentive.  We've visited twice
   for dinner and have not been disappointed at all! We have enjoyed
   Sautéd Crab Fingers, Crab Cakes, Fried Green Tomatoes (topped with
   Crabmeat), Gumbo (made from scratch daily), Fried
   Shrimp/Oysters/Catfish/Crawfish. We highly recommend Captain Brad's!
   Photo courtesy Andrea R/Yelp

